    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The members of the Woman's\nclub will entertain at their annual\nsocial day meeting tomorrow aft\nernoon at the club rooms of the\nchamber of commerce.\n\n\nThe social hours will be spent\nwith progressive five hundred and\nbridge and several prizes will be\nawarded to the successful winners.\n\n\nA large crowd and general good\ntime is expected."
